title: Testimonials Slider 1.2.1 - WordPress Testimonials Plugin
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Testimonials Slider WordPress Plugin is a simple tool to display your customers’ testimonials on your WordPress website in the most vivid and attractive way. You can use any type of feedback to make a trustworthy testimonial with author’s name, photo, company logo and even a URL to the client’s website. Increase credibility of your product showing user experience of your clients and strengthen your reputation with real and sincere testimonials. Testimonials Slider WordPress Plugin Features Full author data Total trust with social profile URL Brands to add weight Smart columns distribution Slider Layout Grid Layout Single templates for client stories Tiled templates for multiple testimonials Visual composer support
